OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a largely cloudy
OL,6,Fmorning with some outbreaks of light
OL,7,Frain and drizzle. Drier through the
OL,8,Fafternoon with some brighter spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping. Freshening northeast
OL,10,Fwinds. Feeling cooler.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will remain dry through
OL,13,Fthe evening and overnight with
OL,14,Fvariable cloud and sunny then clear
OL,15,Fspells. Winds falling light.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FIt will be cool with variable
OL,18,Fcloud and some bright or sunny spells
OL,19,Fat times. Showers pushing south later
OL,20,Fin the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
