OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FEarly
OL,6,Frain on Monday followed by bright
OL,7,Fspells and showers, these continuing
OL,8,Fthrough Tuesday and Wednesday, and
OL,9,Fbecoming heavy and blustery at times.
OL,10,FRemaining cool.
